snippet: Despite seemingly endless waves of attacks from the United States, a plucky but overmatched Antigua and Barbuda squad fought hard before eventually losing to the Americans, 3-1.
abstract: United States men's national soccer team defeats a plucky but overmatched Antigua and Barbuda squad, 3-1, on the road to World Cup qualification.
lead_paragraph: Despite seemingly endless waves of attacks from the United States, a plucky but overmatched Antigua and Barbuda squad fought hard before eventually losing to the Americans, 3-1.

headline.seo: A World Cup Qualifying Victory Lacks Quality for the U.S.
headline.main: A Cup Qualifying Victory Lacks Quality
